{"tid":1359980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[抗爭當課外活動？]唯一一次唔可以兄弟爬山？我有無撚睇錯？","createTime":"2019-07-24T09:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T09:26:25.000Z","uid":40170,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"99bfe1b11a27bb92ea6fda485d28a2653d0ea0af","tid":1359980,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:00:45.000Z","msg":"屌我都要講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「兄弟爬山」就係大家都唔知點做先啱</span></strong></span><br />\n所以先包容所有方法<br />\n咩都試吓<br />\n<br />\n咩叫唔可以兄弟爬山<br />\n可持續社運？<br />\n每一次出嚟行我都想係最後一次行<br />\n我唔係話衝一定即刻贏 <br />\n燒村可以即刻有人回應五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n講吓衝嘅義士都畀人負皮到上天<br />\n係咪遊行行上癮？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">傾文宣 傾有無啲兩邊都接受到嘅做法 傾點先可以集中目標圍／衝 推721上環元朗post 有無咁難呀？ 吓？</span></strong></span><br />\n圍佢地嘅村口重生點好<br />\n將文宣當溪錢灑佢老母又好<br />\n可唔可以傾 但唔好屌 唔好以為只有單一方法可以做好件事得唔撚得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4374b5597858907f2dcb07b30d8c7976b14013","tid":1359980,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:01:07.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d593b9b6c75774b8d3962f626cf20a3b3df4673","tid":1359980,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:02:51.000Z","msg":"高質連登仔係咪出晒去圍黨鐵呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2293431adc725a4a4ab266fc3c6e1dbc86e0fcf6